{"thag2.3:0.1":"Theragatha 2.3 ","thag2.3:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.3:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag2.3:0.4":"Valliyattheragatha ","thag2.3:1.1":"“Makkato pancadvarayam, ","thag2.3:1.2":"kutikayam pasakkiya; ","thag2.3:1.3":"Dvarena anupariyeti, ","thag2.3:1.4":"ghattayanto muhum muhum. ","thag2.3:2.1":"Tittha makkata ma dhavi, ","thag2.3:2.2":"na hi te tam yatha pure; ","thag2.3:2.3":"Niggahitosi pannaya, ","thag2.3:2.4":"neva duram gamissati”ti. ","thag2.3:2.5":"… Valliyo thero …. "}